              <span class="vtl-tog">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vtl-body">
              <p>The mandatory online non-immigrant visa application. Every field matters — errors here cause delays or rejection at the consulate gate. Consistency with your supporting documents is critical.</p>
              <div class="vtl-svc">📋 Our service: Full Visa Filing</div>
              <a href="/book?service=full-filing-usa" class="vtl-cta">Book Now →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="vtl-item">
          <div class="vtl-track">
            <div class="vtl-dot"></div>
            <div class="vtl-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="vtl-content">
            <div class="vtl-header">
              <div class="vtl-title-group">
                <span class="vtl-title">Fee Payment</span>
                <span class="vtl-sub">Day 3–4</span>
              </div>
              <span class="vtl-tog">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vtl-body">
              <p>$185 MRV fee — non-refundable, payable before booking the appointment. Valid at any of the five Indian consulates. Must be paid through the official portal, not third parties.</p>
              <div class="vtl-svc">ℹ️ Included in Full Filing service</div>
              <a href="/book?service=full-filing-usa" class="vtl-cta">Learn More →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 — APPOINTMENT (special) -->
        <div class="vtl-item">
          <div class="vtl-track">
            <div class="vtl-dot vtl-dot-warn"></div>
            <div class="vtl-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="vtl-content">
            <div class="vtl-header">
              <div class="vtl-title-group">
                <span class="vtl-title">Appointment Booking</span>
                <div class="vtl-appt-row">
                  <span class="vtl-appt-badge red">Standard: 400+ day wait</span>
                  <span class="vtl-appt-or">or</span>
                  <span class="vtl-appt-badge green">Express Appointment: 40–60 day wait</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="vtl-tog">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vtl-body">
              <p>The biggest bottleneck in the entire US visa process. Slots at Indian consulates are extremely scarce. Standard booking currently means a 400+ day wait at most locations.</p>
              <p>Our <strong>Express Appointment</strong> service actively monitors slot availability across all five Indian consulates — Mumbai, Delhi, Chennai, Kolkata, and Hyderabad — and secures your date in 40–60 days.</p>
              <div class="vtl-svc">📅 Our service: Express Appointment Booking</div>
              <a href="/book?service=appointment-usa" class="vtl-cta vtl-cta-warn">Beat the Queue →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 5 -->
        <div class="vtl-item">
          <div class="vtl-track">
            <div class="vtl-dot"></div>
            <div class="vtl-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="vtl-content">
            <div class="vtl-header">
              <div class="vtl-title-group">
                <span class="vtl-title">Document Preparation</span>
                <span class="vtl-sub">Use the appointment wait time</span>
              </div>
              <span class="vtl-tog">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vtl-body">
              <p>While waiting for your appointment, use the time to strengthen your document package. Weak documents are the #1 controllable rejection factor. This is where most cases are won or lost.</p>
              <div class="vtl-svc">🔍 Our service: Document Audit</div>
              <a href="/book?service=doc-audit-usa" class="vtl-cta">Audit Your Docs →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 6 -->
        <div class="vtl-item">
          <div class="vtl-track">
            <div class="vtl-dot"></div>
            <div class="vtl-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="vtl-content">
            <div class="vtl-header">
              <div class="vtl-title-group">
                <span class="vtl-title">Visa Interview</span>
                <span class="vtl-sub">Interview day</span>
              </div>
              <span class="vtl-tog">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vtl-body">
              <p>A 2–3 minute conversation that determines everything. First impressions, clarity, and knowing what NOT to say are critical. Officers ask sharp, profile-specific questions. We coach you on every likely scenario beforehand.</p>
              <div class="vtl-svc">🎯 Our service: Interview Preparation</div>
              <a href="/book?service=interview-usa" class="vtl-cta">Prepare Now →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 7 — last, no connector line -->
        <div class="vtl-item vtl-item-last">
          <div class="vtl-track">
            <div class="vtl-dot vtl-dot-green"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="vtl-content">
            <div class="vtl-header">
              <div class="vtl-title-group">
                <span class="vtl-title">Visa Decision</span>
                <span class="vtl-sub vtl-sub-green">3–15 days after interview</span>
              </div>
              <span class="vtl-tog">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vtl-body">
              <p>Passport dispatched with a sticker visa, or administrative processing begins (can take weeks). If refused under 214(b), a recovery reapplication is possible. We analyse the refusal reason and rebuild your case.</p>
              <div class="vtl-svc">🔄 Our service: Rejection Recovery</div>
              <a href="/book?service=rejection-usa" class="vtl-cta vtl-cta-red">Start Recovery →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
